Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:08.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚踏大地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:11.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏醒的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:14.22,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在她的微笑中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:18.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结伴远行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:29.67,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使孤身一人 但却并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:35.44,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来到这个世界 就必然会有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:39.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can smile again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沐浴着阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:44.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can fly away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:50.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界 正在等待你来大显身手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:53.01,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚踏大地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.27,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏醒的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:59.17,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在她的微笑中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:02.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结伴远行（You can smile）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:08.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管何时开始 都不算晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:14.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来出发吧 无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
